<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to The Divine Crustacean!</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/index.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <%- include('partials/header') %>
        <main class="content container-fluid p-0">
            <section class="hero-section text-center py-5 bg-light">
                <div class="container">
                    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to The Divine Crustacean!</h1>
                    <p class="lead">Your ultimate destination for all things crustacean. Join events, meet fellow enthusiasts, and explore the fascinating world of crustaceans.</p>
                    <a href="/events" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Explore Events</a>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="about-us-section py-5">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h2>About Us</h2>
                            <p>At The Divine Crustacean, we are passionate about the diverse and fascinating world of crustaceans. Our mission is to connect crustacean enthusiasts from around the globe, fostering a community where knowledge and appreciation for these incredible creatures can flourish.</p>
                            <p>Whether you're a seasoned expert or a curious newcomer, our platform offers something for everyone. From educational resources to exciting events, we strive to be the ultimate hub for all things crustacean.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
                            <img src="/images/about-us.jpg" alt="About Us" class="img-fluid rounded">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="features-section py-5 bg-light">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2 class="text-center">What You Can Do</h2>
                    <div class="row text-center mt-4">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="feature-box p-4">
                                <img src="/images/join-events.jpg" alt="Join Events" class="img-fluid rounded mb-3">
                                <h3>Join Events</h3>
                                <p>Participate in exciting events and meet fellow crustacean enthusiasts. From local meetups to international conferences, there's always something happening.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="feature-box p-4">
                                <img src="/images/learn.jpg" alt="Learn" class="img-fluid rounded mb-3">
                                <h3>Learn</h3>
                                <p>Tap into the wealth of our community! Our community hosts some very prominent crustacean enthusiasts that are more than happy and capable of sharing their knowledge to help you with any questions or gaps that you may have.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="feature-box p-4">
                                <img src="/images/community.jpg" alt="Community" class="img-fluid rounded mb-3">
                                <h3>Connect</h3>
                                <p>Join our community forums and social media groups to share your experiences, ask questions, and connect with other enthusiasts from around the world.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="call-to-action-section text-center py-5">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2>Ready to Dive In?</h2>
                    <p class="lead">Sign up today and start your journey with The Divine Crustacean. Whether you're looking to learn, participate, or connect, we're here to help you explore the incredible world of crustaceans.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-success btn-lg">Sign Up</a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="/scripts.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
